Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:33.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his friends \Nchased after a big beetle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which appeared suddenly during their journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to recruit him, and in doing \Nso they reached an unknown island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you giant beetle! Join my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will never become...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this beetle as their guardian angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko, a girl who hates pirates and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the people from the same ocean \Nlive on this island called...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kansorn Island where people \Nfrom the East Blue live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also known as Little East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the Amigo Pirates, working on \Norders from the legendary pirate Shiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are heading to Kansorn Island as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Special Presentation Related to the \NMovie! Little East Blue in Danger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reefs surround the island. It's \Ntoo dangerous to speed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here! It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look at her! Nami-sama in \Nperson is there in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's mega cute, way more \Nthan the wanted poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help crying! I'm \Nso happy to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're members of the unofficial \NNami-sama fan club...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Known as Orenami Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orenami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! L...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We love you! Nami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! That's so irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to see Luffy, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's our pleasure, Nami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For God's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop calling me Nami-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Windmill Village so \Nthey must be familiar to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but none of ours were this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That windmill is like a \Nsymbol for Little East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? This is the training hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m here to challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My 2001st win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch break is over! Let's \Nstart afternoon lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-H-He wants to challenge us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! He's not a challenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look! He's \N"Pirate Hunter" Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have your autograph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks just like Kaya's mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd always poke her head \Nout of the window upstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Usopp-san!\N--Hey, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what adventure are you \Ngoing to tell me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of when I fought the \Ngiant goldfish at the South Pole
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was five!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! What first shocked me was \Nthe immense size of its poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so big that I landed on \Nit, thinking it was solid ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so thin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Luigia who lives here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,built this in the style of the \Nmansion that she used to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No way! It wasn't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she used to live in the mansion \Nthat means she's a relative of Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me that you're K-Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?! Who is she! Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of the Straw Hats, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I cook for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At an on-the-sea restaurant in \Nthe East Blue for several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baratie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really from the Baratie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! I'm thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with dishes that Zeff cooks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to steal some idea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,s by going there often around \Nthe time when it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The building is similar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have Zeff's courage so I \Ncouldn't imagine making it on the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still wanted as style similar to his.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I don't have any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I figured out how the \Ndamn geezer cooks the dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Does it taste like Zeff's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. In fact, you're better \Nthan that old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? I can't tell \Nyou how happy that makes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee... even the cook seems happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're from Syrup Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Yasopp's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of. We had a lot of \Ntroubles with his lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad? Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you really live in the mansion there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know if you're from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mansion is not only \Nthe symbol of the village
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's everybody's dream house!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:13:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to live in a mansion \Nlike that since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally made my dream come after \NI ended up being on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means you're not \Nrelated to Kaya at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm known as a cranky princess here so don't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell anybody if you don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, even the granny is bonding with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please watch your step there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange place to walk through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a maze made by nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It connected to different \Nparts of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice but, are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the symbol of Orenami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard because we only \Nhad the poster to draw from!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... I mean... Why is it naked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was decided by consensus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We made sure \Nto get the front, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They let pirates on to the \Nisland which you and my father
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have always been protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them! I hate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys! Let's take this \Nthing to the legendary pirate Shiki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become his brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, we're after the big beetle \Nthat took off from Shiki's hide-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?! Failure is not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry, Big Bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're the captain so you \Nbetter say something about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, he's in the middle of a siesta now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! He's not gonna wake up for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--Don't do it, Colt-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what's gonna happen if you \Nwake him when he's having a siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! We don't wanna die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell could he take a nap at this \Ncrucial moment for us Amigo Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta do it without him \Nthen! Are you ready, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Órale!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's done! We have a \Nsteel cage for the beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It only took you a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! It's a piece of cake for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready for the beetle at any minute now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They might be back \Nwith it at any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a welcome party for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuboshi really wanted this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a party for pirates? \NWhat're they thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're here!\N--The town square is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept saying we were "almost" \Nthere but you made me walk for hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted you to enjoy our \Nisland to the full extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pirate, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even women are into pirates? \NThese are crazy times!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Everybody's into pirates! \NThese are crazy times!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko! You can't talk to \NNami-sama like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! Ouch! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nami-sama! Her father \Nwas killed by pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody, I need your \Nattention! Yes, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Amigo Pirates! This \Nisland is under siege!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna get killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us have the beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beetle?! Why does he know about Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't go to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the big beetle \Nis protecting this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he has nobody to protect, there'll \Nbe no reason for him to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Boss! Stay there! Don't show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They destroyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I represent this island's inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then where's the beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but you can't have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you can have all \Nour money and food and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it all and go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, believe me, we intend to do \Nso! We intend to take everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money, food, and the beetle as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! Couldn't eat another bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the heck are you? What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, Fancy Hat! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant beetle doesn't \Nwant to join a pirate crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Join the crew?! \NYou got me wrong, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a rubberman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit eater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright!\N--We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna fight more, Fancy Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That beetle's gonna fight me again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you ruin that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mucho Needle Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amore! My beloved brother Colt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a rubberman,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you get away with it, senor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's my Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo-hoo-hoo, so melancholy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:23:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is captured by Largo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Sanji also struggle against \Nthe powers of the Net-Net Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the beetle learns that \Nit is the pirates' target,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes a grave decision in \Norder to protect the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Special Presentation Related to the Movie!\NThe Fierce Onslaught of the Amigo Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
